Text: RE Site Visits Peakers Cc Southern Energy has decided NOT to pursue the assets in the MidWest Lincoln Center Wheatland Kim Heinz our project director has notified CSFB of this decision Thanks Original Message From mailto Sent Monday October PM To Subject Re Site Visits Peakers Barbara If you could send me a list of people and their cell phone numbers who are going to the sites as well as exact times that you will be there I would appreciate it Please let me know if you have any other questions Thanks Ben
